text: Si Racha Municipal Stadium () is a multi-purpose stadium in Si Racha, Chonburi, Thailand. It is currently used mostly for football matches. The stadium holds 5,000 people.http://www.chonburihotreportnews.com/2018/08/30-10.html ==References== Category:Multi-purpose stadiums in Thailand Category:Buildings and structures in Chonburi Province Category:Sport in Chonburi Province
